quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  7,58,"Leydi moЖґЖґiri ndin, puЙ—i mayri no yaltira duЕ‹ayee Joomi mayri ; ndin ndi (puЙ—i mun) boni, ndi yaltintaa si wanaa no saЙ—tiri. Ko non Men ЖЃannginirta Aayeeje Й—en woannde yimЙ“e yettooЙ“e [Joomi mun]"
  7,59,"GomЙ—ii Men Nulii Nuuhu e yimЙ“e makko Й“en, o maaki : \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, rewee Alla. ReweteeЙ—o alanaa on ko woori Mo. Min miЙ—o hulani on lepte Г‘alaande mawnde"
  7,60,"HooreeЙ“e mbatu yimЙ“e makko Й“en wi'i : \"Menen meЙ—en yi'e e nder majjere Й“anngunde"
  7,61,"O maaki : \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, majjere (woo) alaa e am ; ko woni min, ko NulaaЙ—o immorde ka JeyЙ—o Winndere nden"
  7,62,"MiЙ—o yottina e mon Nule Joomi am, miЙ—o laaЙ“ana on (reedu), miЙ—o anndi ka Alla ko on anndaa"
  7,63,"E on haawi fii waaju no ari on immorde ka Joomi mon e dow gorko jeyaaЙ—o e mo'on?! Fii yo o jertin on e fii yo on rento, belajo'o, on (heЙ“ay) yurmeende [Alla]"
  7,64,"ЖЃe fenni mo. Men daЙ—ndii mo e Й“en wonnduЙ“e e makko ka laana, Men yooli Й“en fennuЙ“e Aayeeje Amen Й—en. Pellet, Й“e laatino yimЙ“e wumiЙ—uЙ“e"
  7,65,"[Men Nulii] kadi faade e AadinkooЙ“e Й“en, musiЙ—Й—o maЙ“Й“e on Huudi. O maaki : \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, rewee Alla, reweteeЙ—o alanaa on ko woori mo. E on hulataa [Mo]"
  7,66,"HooreeЙ“e mbatu Й“en yedduЙ“e e yimЙ“e makko Й“en wi'i : \"Menen meЙ—en yi'e e Й—ayre, menen meЙ—en sikku maa jeyaaЙ—o e fenooЙ“e Й“en"
  7,67,"O maaki : \"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e am, Й—ayre (woo) alaa e am ; ko woni min, ko NulaaЙ—o immorde ka JeyЙ—o Winndere nden"
